<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 09:11:14 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国海警船进入东海争议海域</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-coast-guard-vessels-enter-disputed-waters-east-china-sea-2024-02-06/</link><description>中国海警周二表示，他们在钓鱼岛（也称为尖阁诸岛）海域进行巡逻。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 08:49:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-coast-guard-vessels-enter-disputed-waters-east-china-sea-2024-02-06/</guid></item><item><title>英国石油公司财报和中国刺激措施提振欧洲股市开盘</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/bp-earnings-china-stimulus-lift-european-stocks-open-2024-02-06/</link><description>欧洲股市周二上涨，受益于石油巨头英国石油公司公布的积极盈利报告以及中国遭受重创的金融市场出台新刺激措施的迹象。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 08:33:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/bp-earnings-china-stimulus-lift-european-stocks-open-2024-02-06/</guid></item><item><title>中国股市因官方支持再度升温而大幅反弹</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-stocks-rebound-sharply-renewed-talk-official-support-2024-02-06/</link><description>周二，遭受重创的中国股市创下两年来最大单日涨幅，一系列信号表明当局正在加强支持低迷市场的决心，人民币汇率也随之上涨。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 08:24:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-stocks-rebound-sharply-renewed-talk-official-support-2024-02-06/</guid></item><item><title>中国船只在马尔代夫用于科学研究-外交部</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-vessel-maldives-being-used-scientific-research-foreign-ministry-2024-02-06/</link><description>中国外交部周二表示，一艘中国船只停靠马尔代夫港口进行的研究完全出于和平目的并增进科学认识，该船即将抵达这个岛国。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 07:36:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-vessel-maldives-being-used-scientific-research-foreign-ministry-2024-02-06/</guid></item><item><title>脱北者称口粮减少和市场依赖为由</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korea-defectors-cite-dwindling-food-rations-market-reliance-study-2024-02-06/</link><description>首尔统一部发布的一项研究显示，过去十年在韩国重新定居的大多数朝鲜人表示，他们从未在这个孤立的国家获得过政府口粮，不得不依靠非正式市场生存。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 07:04:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korea-defectors-cite-dwindling-food-rations-market-reliance-study-2024-02-06/</guid></item><item><title>中国市场因政策提振前景而跃升</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/view-china-markets-leap-prospect-policy-boost-2024-02-06/</link><description>周二，中国股市创下 14 个月以来的最大涨幅，人民币上涨，原因是国家支持市场的进一步迹象以及国家主席习近平将与金融监管机构讨论市场的新闻报道。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 06:55:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/view-china-markets-leap-prospect-policy-boost-2024-02-06/</guid></item><item><title>中国监管机构出台更多卖空限制措施</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-regulator-unveils-more-curbs-short-selling-2024-02-06/</link><description>中国证券监管机构周二表示，将暂停券商借入股票进行借贷，并限制所谓的证券再融资规模，作为进一步遏制卖空行为的一部分。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 05:15:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-regulator-unveils-more-curbs-short-selling-2024-02-06/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟旨在就实现绿色工业雄心的关键路径达成一致</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/climate-energy/eu-aims-agree-key-path-towards-green-industry-ambitions-2024-02-06/</link><description>欧盟政策制定者希望周二达成新规则，促进太阳能、风能、燃料电池和其他清洁技术设备的国内生产，以确保其行业能够与中国和美国竞争对手竞争。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 05:03:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/climate-energy/eu-aims-agree-key-path-towards-green-industry-ambitions-2024-02-06/</guid></item><item><title>梅西希望在香港队表现不佳后参加东京友谊赛</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/messi-hopes-play-tokyo-friendly-after-hong-kong-letdown-2024-02-06/</link><description>周末缺席比赛，令众多香港球迷失望后，莱昂内尔·梅西(Lionel Messi)保留了参加迈阿密国际队在东京的友谊赛的可能性，称他离开时比几天前“好多了” 。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 05:03:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/messi-hopes-play-tokyo-friendly-after-hong-kong-letdown-2024-02-06/</guid></item><item><title>中国表示反对并打击一切形式的网络攻击</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-it-opposes-cracks-down-all-forms-cyberattacks-2024-02-06/</link><description>中国驻菲律宾大使馆表示，中国政府不会容忍任何形式的网络攻击，也不会允许任何国家和个人利用中国基础设施从事此类非法活动。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 03:34:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-it-opposes-cracks-down-all-forms-cyberattacks-2024-02-06/</guid></item><item><title>中国股市因救援行动而飙升；美元，收益率稳定</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-02-06/</link><description>周二，亚洲股市随着中国股市的上涨而大幅上涨，因为北京方面加大力度为低迷的市场提供支撑，但其他地区的投资者则持谨慎态度，因为对美联储近期降息的押注减少。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 02:35:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-02-06/</guid></item><item><title>独家：台湾盟友危地马拉考虑与中国建立商业关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/taiwan-ally-guatemala-mulls-commercial-ties-with-china-foreign-minister-says-2024-02-06/</link><description>中美洲国家危地马拉外交部长周一告诉路透社，危地马拉正在考虑与中国建立正式贸易关系，但计划维持与台湾的现有关系。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 02:28:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/taiwan-ally-guatemala-mulls-commercial-ties-with-china-foreign-minister-says-2024-02-06/</guid></item><item><title>雪、冰阻碍了数百万中国人春节前的回家之旅</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/icy-weather-impedes-travellers-china-home-bound-new-year-festivities-2024-02-06/</link><description>冻雨、雪和冰使中国中部和东部地区的许多人的回家之路变得复杂，数十亿人在春节前在寒冷的天气中出行。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 02:21:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/icy-weather-impedes-travellers-china-home-bound-new-year-festivities-2024-02-06/</guid></item><item><title>日本SMBC聘请前瑞士信贷中国区总裁斯托尔</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/japans-smbc-hires-former-credit-suisse-china-boss-stoehr-2024-02-06/</link><description>日本三井住友银行（SMBC）周二表示，已聘请前瑞士信贷中国区总裁卡斯滕·斯托尔（Carsten Stoehr）担任亚太区副总裁。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 02:15:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/japans-smbc-hires-former-credit-suisse-china-boss-stoehr-2024-02-06/</guid></item><item><title>美元波动，澳元因加息前景而上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-firms-near-3-month-high-rate-cut-bets-dwindle-2024-02-06/</link><description>周二美元小幅走低，但仍距三个月高点不远，而在央行表示可能需要加息以抑制通胀后澳元上涨。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 01:47:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-firms-near-3-month-high-rate-cut-bets-dwindle-2024-02-06/</guid></item></channel></rss>